{"tid":2080143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本神奈川縣大和市立例禁止民眾邊行邊看手機","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T09:11:50.000Z","uid":241764,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"379cb86b00d2abf6f2d4463cb56e5fef8f10b6fb","tid":2080143,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"日本神奈川縣大和市議會通過法例，禁止行人邊行邊看手機，下月1日起生效，是全日本首個訂立類似法例的地方。<br />\n<br />\n條例規定，在市內的道路、公園等公共場所使用智能手機時，要避免妨礙他人通行，停下腳步才使用。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534271-20200626.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534271-20200626.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h2t2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=3edb7247\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534271-20200626.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1f811aa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534271-20200626.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"78fedf65661229cedc90a6347686a7ee3fec7f8c","tid":2080143,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"德政"},{"pid":"96e94d7abbaed06a217dc4900c7e59ea32073c6c","tid":2080143,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"停係路中間用，又行兩步，又停係路中間用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af88a03576dfb38817285b295cfa46e6b4e6bd4","tid":2080143,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96e94d7abbaed06a217dc4900c7e59ea32073c6c","tid":2080143,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:39:00.000Z","msg":"停係路中間用，又行兩步，又停係路中間用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr